            date="2006-05-17",
            changesNeeded=false,
            comments="Looks fine.")
public interface Vectorizable
extends CloneableSerializable
    The Vectorizable interface is an interface for an object that can be converted to and from a Vector.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Justin Basilico, Kevin R. Dixon
